ICBM is a two-compartment model considering one young (Yt) and one old (Ot) soil carbon pool. The calculations were made using the following equations (from Eqs. 6 and 7 in [50]), adapted to handle three types of biomass inputs:Y[AG, BG, LG]t=(Y[AG, BG, L]t-1+i[AG, BG, LG]t-1)e-kyre\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
